What you need to know:

From the Biblical times of Samson and Delilah, authorities have preferred using women to entrap dangerous men.While some may argue it is a sexist notion to use women as a tool in security practice, experts say with professionalism it is the perfect tool.In most cases, women used as bait are usually accomplices in the crimes of the gangsters with a knowledge of their movement and activities.Men tend to focus on the sexual favours they could get from the woman in the long run causing them lower their guard.